root: ^Finally you wake up, how you sleep last night?
^I feel terrible, My head is killing me. I'm sorry, who are you?
^My name is Rose and you are in Oppidum our little town.
^How did I got here, I can't remember anything from last night.
^Ren found you unconscious in the road and bring you here.
^Our guard, don't worry right now, go talk to Sofia she would explain you everything.
